    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people care, but it doesn't change the reality. the debt is still there, the exams are still coming, and i'm still just... empty. it feels like the more i try to \"find hope,\" the more exhausted i get. it's like a cycle i can't break. honestly, the idea of just not having to deal with any of this anymore... it's the only thing that feels peaceful.",
